arChildNodes.szComment:
Neyrelle bends down, retrieves an item, and dusts it off. The cracking of a BRANCH causes Neyrelle and the Player to whip their heads around.
Player swiftly gets into their battle stance. 
A figure steps out of the shadows: it’s ERU! He looks weakened and pathetic. He’s outlined by a corrupt energy. 
He eyes the Player's battle stance.
The player lunges forward but is stopped by Neyrelle’s hand.
Darkened corrupted spirit energy swarms around Eru. He winces.
Neyrelle takes a cautious step towards Eru.
Eru is a flash of power now, surging in his anger.
Blackened spirit energy coruscates around his body.
The Player protectively stands between Neyrelle and Eru.
Leading up to a fight between Eru and the Player
